# Ignore all ...
/*

# ... but track specific files / folders: 

# General files
!.gitignore
!/README.md
!/LICENSE
!/.screenshot.png

# DDEV config and provider script
!/.ddev
/.ddev/*
!/.ddev/config.yaml
!/.ddev/providers
/.ddev/providers/*
